SQL_STMT_U.val: select PER.ID from :1/*PCTAOP*/ TAL (nolock) inner join :2/*PCPROCOP*/ POP (nolock) on POP.OP = TAL.OP and POP.CLASS_HIERARQ between TAL.CLASS_HIERARQ_INI and TAL.CLASS_HIERARQ_FIN and POP.CLASS_PROCESSO = TAL.CLASS_PROCESSO inner join TE_QUESTXPROC QXP (nolock) on QXP.PROCESSO = POP.PROCESS_ITEM inner join TE_QUESTXPERG QXE (nolock) on QXE.QUESTIONARIO = QXP.QUESTIONARIO inner join TE_PERGUNTA PER (nolock) on PER.ID = QXE.PERGUNTA left join TE_PERGUNTAXUN UN (nolock) ON UN.Id_Pergunta = PER.Id where PER.ATIVA = 1 and TAL.OP = :3 and TAL.TALAO = :4 and (UN.Un_Negocio = ':5' OR UN.Un_Negocio IS NULL)
